Phrase en Français: “Elite training” is a section of the Field Manual which caters to dauntless adventurers who wish to engage in a more grueling test of their mettle.${prompt}

Phrase en Anglais: “Elite training” is a section of the Field Manual which caters to dauntless adventurers who wish to engage in a more grueling test of their mettle.${prompt}
Phrase en Français: To participate in elite training regimes, you must acquire chapter transcripts, for which tabs are required.${prompt}

Phrase en Anglais: To participate in elite training regimes, you must acquire chapter transcripts, for which tabs are required.${prompt}
Phrase en Français: Trading ${item-plural: 35[2]}, gil, or a piece of equipment at designated locations (while in possession of a chapter transcript) will trigger the commencement of your training.${prompt}

Phrase en Anglais: Trading ${item-plural: 35[2]}, gil, or a piece of equipment at designated locations (while in possession of a chapter transcript) will trigger the commencement of your training.${prompt}
Phrase en Français: Traded items will not be returned to you. You will, however, be furnished with rewards of correlating value upon the successful completion of each elite training regime.${prompt}

Phrase en Anglais: Traded items will not be returned to you. You will, however, be furnished with rewards of correlating value upon the successful completion of each elite training regime.${prompt}
Phrase en Français: Even within elite training, there are regimes of varying difficulty. The trade limit for each succeeding chapter will be greater than the last, and the training objective more challenging.

Phrase en Anglais: Even within elite training, there are regimes of varying difficulty. The trade limit for each succeeding chapter will be greater than the last, and the training objective more challenging.
Phrase en Français: For safety reasons, all participants are recommended to be well prepared.${prompt}

Phrase en Anglais: For safety reasons, all participants are recommended to be well prepared.${prompt}
Phrase en Français: Lastly, we at the A.M.A.N. recognize the importance of rest and recuperation as part of a healthy adventuring lifestyle. Therefore, a mandatory cool-down period will be imposed upon all adventurers following the completion of an elite training regime. Until this time has elapsed, you will be unable to undertake further training, even if a chapter transcript is in your possession.${prompt}

Phrase en Français: You've recovered one of the long-lost mog tablets!

Phrase en Anglais: You've recovered one of the long-lost mog tablets!
Phrase en Français: You should share the news of your discovery with the Explorer Moogle in Ru'Lude Gardens.

Phrase en Anglais: You should share the news of your discovery with the Explorer Moogle in Ru'Lude Gardens.

Phrase en Français: You've heard the tale of the mog tablets, haven't you?

Phrase en Anglais: You've heard the tale of the mog tablets, haven't you?
Phrase en Français: If any of them turn up in your travels, promise you'll let me know, kupo!${prompt}

Phrase en Anglais: If any of them turn up in your travels, promise you'll let me know, kupo!${prompt}

Phrase en Français: Thanks to your efforts, the mog tablets have been recovered, and their magic freed to spread happiness and joy across the realm!

Phrase en Anglais: Thanks to your efforts, the mog tablets have been recovered, and their magic freed to spread happiness and joy across the realm!
Phrase en Français: You are truly a friend to all mooglekind, kupo!${prompt}

Phrase en Anglais: You are truly a friend to all mooglekind, kupo!${prompt}
Phrase en Français: Oh no! What a shame, kupo!

Phrase en Anglais: Oh no! What a shame, kupo!
Phrase en Français: The mog tablets that were recovered have been scattered to the ends of Vana'diel once more...${prompt}

Phrase en Anglais: The mog tablets that were recovered have been scattered to the ends of Vana'diel once more...${prompt}

Phrase en Français: What's a mog tablet!? What's a mog tablet, you say!?

Phrase en Anglais: What's a mog tablet!? What's a mog tablet, you say!?
Phrase en Français: Why, only the most awesome, amazing artifact in the annals of moogle history, that's what, kupo!${prompt}

Phrase en Anglais: Why, only the most awesome, amazing artifact in the annals of moogle history, that's what, kupo!${prompt}
Phrase en Français: There's eleven of them in all, to be exact, scattered to the far reaches of Vana'diel and just waiting to be discovered by brave adventurers like you!${prompt}

Phrase en Anglais: There's eleven of them in all, to be exact, scattered to the far reaches of Vana'diel and just waiting to be discovered by brave adventurers like you!${prompt}
Phrase en Français: What happens if you find them? I thought you'd never ask, kupo!

Phrase en Anglais: What happens if you find them? I thought you'd never ask, kupo!
Phrase en Français: Each tablet is inscribed with an ancient moogle poem of joy, and legend has it that if all are found, the ancient moogle magic of King Kupofried the Great will be released once more, spreading joy and happiness through all the land!${prompt}

Phrase en Anglais: Each tablet is inscribed with an ancient moogle poem of joy, and legend has it that if all are found, the ancient moogle magic of King Kupofried the Great will be released once more, spreading joy and happiness through all the land!${prompt}
Phrase en Français: We explorer moogles have made it our life's work to recover the tablets and unlock their powers.

Phrase en Anglais: We explorer moogles have made it our life's work to recover the tablets and unlock their powers.
Phrase en Français: But with these short legs and little-bitty wings, we can't do it alone, kupo!${prompt}

Phrase en Anglais: But with these short legs and little-bitty wings, we can't do it alone, kupo!${prompt}
Phrase en Français: There! I've whipped up a spell that will instantly transport any tablets you find back here to me.

Phrase en Anglais: There! I've whipped up a spell that will instantly transport any tablets you find back here to me.
Phrase en Français: Come back if you find anything, and happy exploring, kupo!${prompt}

Phrase en Anglais: Come back if you find anything, and happy exploring, kupo!${prompt}
Phrase en Français: Just sit right back and I'll tell you the tale, kupo.

Phrase en Anglais: Just sit right back and I'll tell you the tale, kupo.
Phrase en Français: Many, many ages past, we moogles had our own glorious kingdom.

Phrase en Anglais: Many, many ages past, we moogles had our own glorious kingdom.
Phrase en Français: It was truly the peak of moogle civilization, a veritable golden age for all mooglekind!${prompt}

Phrase en Anglais: It was truly the peak of moogle civilization, a veritable golden age for all mooglekind!${prompt}
Phrase en Français: The seventh king of this great nation was the wise and kindly King Kupofried, a masterful magician famed as the father of the fantastic moogle magic that survives to this very day, kupo!${prompt}

Phrase en Anglais: The seventh king of this great nation was the wise and kindly King Kupofried, a masterful magician famed as the father of the fantastic moogle magic that survives to this very day, kupo!${prompt}
Phrase en Français: In his later years, King Kupofried embarked on what would become the greatest work of his illustrious reign.

Phrase en Anglais: In his later years, King Kupofried embarked on what would become the greatest work of his illustrious reign.
Phrase en Français: Seeking to pass down the prosperity of his kingdom to future generations, he inscribed eleven incantations of moogle joy and happiness onto eleven stone tablets.${prompt}

Phrase en Anglais: Seeking to pass down the prosperity of his kingdom to future generations, he inscribed eleven incantations of moogle joy and happiness onto eleven stone tablets.${prompt}
Phrase en Français: Sadly, the kindly king's intentions went unappreciated by his selfish sons and daughters, and many a fierce feud broke out over who would inherit these relics, kupo...${prompt}

Phrase en Anglais: Sadly, the kindly king's intentions went unappreciated by his selfish sons and daughters, and many a fierce feud broke out over who would inherit these relics, kupo...${prompt}

Phrase en Français: How could the poems that he had composed out of pure love and joy become the root of such strife?${prompt}

Phrase en Anglais: How could the poems that he had composed out of pure love and joy become the root of such strife?${prompt}
Phrase en Français: In his despair, the king commanded his minion bats to scatter the tablets to the far corners of the world, where they would be seen by moogle eyes no more.${prompt}

Phrase en Anglais: In his despair, the king commanded his minion bats to scatter the tablets to the far corners of the world, where they would be seen by moogle eyes no more.${prompt}
Phrase en Français: “Alas! I only wanted my children to be happy, kupo,” he lamented, and flew away on his tiny yet majestic wings, never to be seen in his kingdom again.${prompt}

Phrase en Anglais: “Alas! I only wanted my children to be happy, kupo,” he lamented, and flew away on his tiny yet majestic wings, never to be seen in his kingdom again.${prompt}
Phrase en Français: Left without its wise monarch, the once-glorious moogle kingdom fractured into warring tribes, falling into unrest...and, eventually, ruin.

Phrase en Anglais: Left without its wise monarch, the once-glorious moogle kingdom fractured into warring tribes, falling into unrest...and, eventually, ruin.
Phrase en Français: A tragic tale, don't you think, kupo?${prompt}

Phrase en Anglais: A tragic tale, don't you think, kupo?${prompt}
Phrase en Français: We explorer moogles are the proud descendants of King Kupofried, living only to bring our last great monarch's unrealized dream to fruition.

Phrase en Anglais: We explorer moogles are the proud descendants of King Kupofried, living only to bring our last great monarch's unrealized dream to fruition.
Phrase en Français: We will--we must!--find the mog tablets and bring true joy and happiness to this world!${prompt}

Phrase en Anglais: We will--we must!--find the mog tablets and bring true joy and happiness to this world!${prompt}

Phrase en Anglais: It appears that ${number: 0} moogle ${choice-plurality: 0}[tablet has/tablets have] already been found, kupo.${prompt}

Phrase en Anglais: It's not too late for you to stake your claim, kupo!${prompt}

Phrase en Anglais: All eleven mog tablets have been recovered and restored to their rightful place at the altar of King Kupofried!${prompt}

Phrase en Anglais: Can you feel the ancient moogle magic in the air?

Phrase en Anglais: You can now bask in the benefits of this Super Kupower...${prompt}

Phrase en Français: The Voidwatch is a fellowship of men and women come together to defend the world from extradimensional invaders called “Voidwalkers.” Driven only by an insatiable appetite for destruction, these fell horrors roam the space between dimensions, ever seeking to enter and plunge Vana'diel into chaos.${prompt}
